The Flash (2014) - Season 1 - Episode 8 (WEB-DL - 1080p)
--------------------------------------------------------

THE FLASH is a fast-paced super hero drama that follows the high-speed
adventures of Central City Police scientist Barry Allen, an everyday guy
with the heart of a hero and the genuine desire to help others. When an
unexpected accident at the S.T.A.R. Labs Particle Accelerator facility
strikes Barry, he finds himself suddenly charged with the incredible
power to move at super speeds. While Barry has always been a hero in
his soul, his newfound powers have finally given him the ability to
act like one. With the help of the research team at S.T.A.R. Labs,
Barry begins testing the limits of his evolving powers and using
them to stop crime. With a winning personality and a smile on his
face, Barry Allen - aka The Flash - is finally moving forward
in life... very, very fast!

Produced by DC Entertainment and Warner Bros. Television.


In the first part of the epic crossover event with The Flash
and Arrow, Barry is thrilled when Oliver, Felicity and Diggle
join him in Central City to help stop a meta-human.
